---
---

<section style="background: var(--navy, #0B1029); padding: var(--section-y) var(--gutter);">
  <div class="manifesto-grid">
    <!-- Left: copy -->
    <div class="manifesto-copy">
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: var(--ls-eyebrow); text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--orange, #E8670A); margin: 0 0 16px;">WHY MEN CHOOSE US</p>
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px); color: #FFFFFF; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: var(--lh-heading); margin: 0 0 24px;">Your labs might be normal. You still don't feel right.</h2>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 17px); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.80); line-height: var(--lh-body); margin: 0 0 20px;">
        "Normal" lab ranges are built for the average of a population — not for you. A provider who spends 60 minutes with you can see the difference between a number on a page and how you actually feel.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 17px); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.80); line-height: var(--lh-body); margin: 0 0 32px;">
        We do bloodwork and results in the same visit. No waiting. No referrals. No six-week follow-up to discuss what you already know: something is off.
      </p>

      <!-- Blockquote -->
      <blockquote style="border-left: 3px solid var(--orange, #E8670A); padding: 0 0 0 20px; margin: 0 0 36px;">
        <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); line-height: 1.65; font-style: italic; margin: 0 0 10px;">
          "I went in skeptical. Came out with a protocol same day. Six weeks later I feel like myself again — better sleep, better mood, actually looking forward to the gym."
        </p>
        <cite style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">— James T., 48, Norfolk</cite>
      </blockquote>

      <a href="#hero-form" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 56px; padding: 0 36px; background: var(--orange, #E8670A); color: #FFFFFF; font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; border-radius: var(--radius-pill, 999px); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: var(--shadow-cta);">
        BOOK MY NO-COST VISIT
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: image -->
    <div class="manifesto-image">
      <img src="/images/cro/mwc-team.webp" alt="Men's Wellness Centers providers" loading="lazy" style="width: 100%; height: 480px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 24px; display: block;" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
